The '''Great Maze of Lok''', also know as '''the Labyrinth''', was a mysterious square maze upon the barren surface of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Lok/Legends|Lok]].

==Description==
The maze had several entrances and many dead ends, but those who found their way to the middle were rewarded by the sight of a small oasis, with four palm-like [[Tree/Legends|trees]] and park benches surrounding a clear-[[Water/Legends|water]] pool. A mysterious gardener maintained the oasis.<ref name="SWG:TGMoL" />

The Great Maze was also an obstacle which racers had to drive through in order to complete the [[Lok Marathon]].<ref name="SWG:LM">{{SWGcite|exp=JtL|type=other}}Swoop race track: "Lok Marathon" on Lok</ref>

==History==
The maze was built a long time before the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] by a visiting noble on a hunting expedition.<ref name="SWG:TGMoL" />

After the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], the Great Maze of Lok became the scene of fighting between [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] and [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] operatives.<ref name="SWG:P28">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=other}}Publish 28</ref><ref name="DC">{{SonyCite|url=en_US/players/content.vm?id=66864&resource=features|text=Duty Calls!}}</ref> In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]],<ref name="SWG_timeline">{{SWG_timeline}}</ref> a [[Spacer/Legends|spacer]] managed to reach the center of the Labyrinth and collected a [[Vibroknuckler/Legends|knuckler]] left behind.<ref name="SWG:RMWMII">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=collection|Rare Melee Weapons Mark II}}</ref> Around the same time, a member of [[Nym/Legends|Nym's]] [[Lok Revenants/Legends|Revenants]], [[Rei Reeven]], got injured in the maze. [[Ralia Reeven]], Nym's [[Quartermaster/Legends|quartermaster]], dispatched a spacer to deliver medical supplies to rescue him.<ref name="SWG:SM">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=general|Save Me|Lok}}</ref>

